<p>Trying to open this page <code>http://localhost/tungkal/tampilkan/curah/hujan</code>. And it turn to be trouble, the "theme-main.css" return "404 Not Found". Because it's accessing : <code>http://localhost/tungkal/tampilkan/curah/css/theme-main.css</code> rather than <code>http://localhost/tungkal/css/theme-main.css #correct address</code>. This also happen on <code>&lt;a&gt; tag</code> , <code>&lt;img&gt; tag</code> and other, but return correctly using <code>php include()</code>.</p>  <p>This is source code of tampilkan.php :</p>  <pre><code>&lt;html&gt; &lt;head&gt; &lt;link href="./css/theme-main.css" rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" /&gt; &lt;/head&gt; &lt;body&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=\"./sample\"&gt;test&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;/body&gt; &lt;/html&gt; </code></pre>  <p>This is my .htaccess file :</p>  <pre><code>RewriteOptions inherit Options -Indexes  RewriteEngine On RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d RewriteRule ^tampilkan/(.*)/(.*)$ tampilkan.php?q1=$1&amp;q2=$2  RewriteEngine On RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME} !-d RewriteCond %{REQUEST_FILENAME}.php -f RewriteRule ^(.*)$ $1.php </code></pre>